lyrics:
Verse 1:
Brush, brush, smile big
Brush bugs away
Clean all over
Be happy!

Chorus:

Brush your teeth
Fight the bugs
Keep them clean
Smile bright!

Verse 2:
Brush bottom nice
Bugs don’t stay
Smooth like silk

Verse 3:
Brush up on top
Bright white, yay!

Chorus:
Brush your teeth
Fight the bugs
Keep them clean
Smile bright!

Verse 4:
Brush day and night
No more bugs!
Smiles fresh and bright
